\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 What Flightplan Is\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Flightplan is a sprint-velocity tracker for AI-pair-programming sessions.
\f1\b0  It measures tokens-per-session as a proxy for how much work an agent can do inside a Pro/Max plan window, and learns the user's real burn rate over time so the agent can plan its own scope against a sprint budget.\
This sentence belongs at the top of the README, the npm description, and any eval brief.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
